message.body: I'm leaving work
Man. I can't wait for this project to be over. You need a break! Come straight here?
Oh my god! My night nurse Kwame just resigned too!
This is too much! I walk into craziness this morning! I'm exhausted already.
I don't know if you told me about him.
I don't know. He was a good one. I did my first and only night shift with him.
Wait. You did more than one night shift
Also look what Ramez gave me
I only did one night shift on my own as the primary nurse. That looks cool. But it's in Devon. That's random.
There's public transportation to there
I know. It's like two stops past Villanova. I just thought that the mainline was random. I guess they have a lot of Egyptians there.
Yeah I guess so
Ooh my god! Tian is such a bitch! I went up to five to say goodbye to Nicole. I said I would miss her. As I was walking away I could have sworn I heard her say she's not gonna miss you. Ugh!
This bitch.
Haha
I'm leaving late again
Ok
I miss you
I miss you too
I would love to do that
